继《神秘海域2》开发后，顽皮狗将团队分成两支，同时开发项目。一支团队制作《[[神秘海域3：德雷克的诡计|神秘海域3：德雷克的诡计]]》，斯特拉利和[[尼尔·德鲁克曼|尼尔·德鲁克曼]]则应伊万·威尔斯和克里斯托夫·巴莱斯特拉要求，带领另一支团队开发新游戏；斯特拉利能获任担当总监领导项目，应归于他的经验与既往项目成果<ref name="New Tricks">{{cite web |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2012/02/22/the-past-present-and-future-of-naughty-dog-an-interview-with-the-co-presidents.aspx |title=New Tricks: An Interview With Naughty Dog's Co-Presidents |last=Hansen |first=Ben |work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |publisher=[[GameStop|GameStop]] |date=February 22, 2012 |accessdate=July 6, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6VOeIaJhr?url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/features/archive/2012/02/22/the-past-present-and-future-of-naughty-dog-an-interview-with-the-co-presidents.aspx |archivedate=2015-01-07 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。他们原打算开发杰克与达斯特新作，但团队认为他们“现时不为系列爱好者服务”，而决定制作一款[[知识产权|新游戏]]，题为《[[最后生还者|最后生还者]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/naughty-dog-reveals-how-axed-jack-and-daxter-reboot-led-to-the-last-of-us/1100-6415331/ |title=Naughty Dog reveals how axed Jack and Daxter reboot led to The Last of Us |last=Gaston |first=Martin |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]. [[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]] |date=October 4, 2013 |accessdate=July 6, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YOL3TIlI?url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/naughty-dog-reveals-how-axed-jack-and-daxter-reboot-led-to-the-last-of-us/1100-6415331/ |archivedate=2015-05-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

斯特拉利和德鲁克曼曾在《神秘海域2》中合作过，发现彼此兴趣相投。二人在《最后生还者》开发中常调侃彼此关系“好似结婚”——他们许多想法相异，但最终愿望是实现同个目标<ref name="Best Film" />。斯特拉利负责《最后生还者》的游戏系统<ref name="Best Film">{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/features/the-last-of-us |title=The Last of Us – The Best Film Of The Year (That Wasn't Actually A Film) |work=[[帝國雜誌|Empire]] |publisher=[[Bauer_Media_Group|Bauer Media Group]] |date=December 18, 2013 |accessdate=July 6, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6VZnLkRLE?url=http://www.empireonline.com/features/the-last-of-us |archivedate=2015-01-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，但在最后几周中，有部门忙于其他任务时，他会自己承担职分。比如斯特拉利亲手整理游戏培训屏幕上的文稿；首席美术师纳特·威尔斯对此感到意外，称“我从没听过游戏总监干这活！那像是个…实习任务”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gamasutra.com/view/news/196409/The_Last_of_Us_art_director_talks_egoless_game_development.php |title=The Last of Us art director talks ego-less game development |last=Ligman |first=Kris |work=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] |publisher=[[UBM_plc|UBM plc]] |date=July 16, 2013 |accessdate=July 6, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6VdvXm9Sm?url=http://gamasutra.com/view/news/196409/The_Last_of_Us_art_director_talks_egoless_game_development.php |archivedate=2015-01-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。斯特拉利在[[电子游戏展|电子游戏展]]2012的索尼新闻发布会上展示了游戏演示，而他台上的站姿在[[網路爆紅|网络上爆红]]，被称作“这个布鲁斯”（The Burce）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.naughtydog.com/site/post/the_last_of_us_presents_the_bruce/ |title=The Last of Us presents The Bruce |last=Paul |first=Jason |publisher=[[顽皮狗|Naughty Dog]]. [[索尼電腦娛樂|Sony Computer Entertainment]] |date=June 12, 2012 |accessdate=July 7, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ZosYQXWG?url=http://www.naughtydog.com/site/post/the_last_of_us_presents_the_bruce/ |archivedate=2015-07-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。游戏于2013年6月14日发行并获媒体好评<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/410928/the-last-of-us-review-round-up-easily-naughty-dogs-finest-moment |title=The Last of Us review round-up: 'Easily Naughty Dog's finest moment' |last=Hussain |first=Tamoor |work=[[电脑与电子游戏|Computer and Video Games]] |publisher=[[Future_plc|Future plc]] |date=June 5, 2013 |accessdate=July 6, 2015 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608062740/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/410928/the-last-of-us-review-round-up-easily-naughty-dogs-finest-moment |archivedate=June 8, 2013 }}</ref>。《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》因斯特拉利和德鲁克曼的创作，将二人提名最佳导演；该奖最终由《[[史丹利的寓言|史丹利的寓言]]》（2013）的导演戴维·弗雷登取得<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/10542023/Telegraph-Video-Game-Awards-2013.html |title=Telegraph Video Game Awards 2013 |last=Hoggins |first=Tom |work=[[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] |publisher=[[電訊媒體集團|Telegraph Media Group]] |location=London |date=December 31, 2013 |accessdate=July 6, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YDIHEcRe?url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/10542023/Telegraph-Video-Game-Awards-2013.html |archivedate=2015-05-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。斯特拉利此后继续担任下载[[资料片|资料片]]《[[最后生还者：遗落|最后生还者：遗落]]》的总监<ref name="TLOULB">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/videos/the-last-of-us-developers-talk-left-behind-dlc-spo/2300-6417282/ |title=The Last of Us Developers Talk Left Behind DLC [SPOILERS] |last=Jayne |first=Jeremy |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]. [[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]] |date=February 17, 2014 |accessdate=July 6, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YPb8rZlU?url=http://www.gamespot.com/videos/the-last-of-us-developers-talk-left-behind-dlc-spo/2300-6417282/ |archivedate=2015-05-10 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

亨尼格在2014年3月离开顽皮狗后，消息宣布斯特拉利和德鲁克曼将分别担任《[[神秘海域4：盗贼末路|神秘海域4：盗贼末路]]》的游戏总监与创意总监<ref name="UC4">{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2014/06/02/the-last-of-us-directors-are-officially-heading-up-uncharted-4 |title=The Last of Us' Directors Are Officially Heading Up Uncharted 4 |last=Moriarty |first=Colin |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]. [[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]] |date=June 2, 2014 |accessdate=July 6, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YPIOgcbt?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/06/02/the-last-of-us-directors-are-officially-heading-up-uncharted-4 |archivedate=2015-05-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。起初报道称汉尼恩是遭斯特拉利和德鲁克曼“逼走”，但随后联合总裁伊万和克里斯托弗否认了该说法<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2014/03/05/uncharted-ps4-writer-amy-hennig-leaves-naughty-dog |title=Uncharted PS4 Writer Amy Hennig Leaves Naughty Dog |last=Dyer |first=Mitch |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]. [[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]] |date=March 4, 2014 |accessdate=July 6, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YPISoWEq?url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/03/05/uncharted-ps4-writer-amy-hennig-leaves-naughty-dog |archivedate=2015-05-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。斯特拉利在2014年12月的[[PlayStation_Experience|PlayStation Experience]]，以及2015年6月的[[E3_2015|电子游戏展]]上，展出了《神秘海域4》的游戏演示<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/6/20/8817971/uncharted-4-e3-demo-blooper-snafu-gaffe |title=Why Uncharted 4's action-packed demo began with 30 seconds of standing around |last=Good |first=Owen S. |work=[[Polygon|Polygon]] |publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]] |date=June 20, 2015 |accessdate=July 6, 2015 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ZotGvdAX?url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/6/20/8817971/uncharted-4-e3-demo-blooper-snafu-gaffe |archivedate=2015-07-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

